<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Returns<sp/>expression<sp/>unevaluated<sp/>as<sp/>data</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Useful<sp/>for<sp/>symbolic<sp/>computation</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>`define`<sp/>(planned)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```lisp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">(define<sp/>name<sp/>value)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">(define<sp/>(name<sp/>params...)<sp/>body)<sp/><sp/>;<sp/>Function<sp/>sugar</highlight></codeline>
