<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Security<sp/>Model</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Threat<sp/>Model</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**Untrusted<sp/>Computation**:<sp/>Servers<sp/>may<sp/>try<sp/>to<sp/>extract<sp/>private<sp/>data</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>**Side<sp/>Channels**:<sp/>Timing<sp/>or<sp/>pattern<sp/>analysis<sp/>attacks</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>**Malicious<sp/>Optimization**:<sp/>Servers<sp/>return<sp/>incorrect<sp/>results</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>**Complexity<sp/>Attacks**:<sp/>DoS<sp/>through<sp/>expensive<sp/>computations</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Security<sp/>Properties</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**Data<sp/>Privacy**:<sp/>Holes<sp/>never<sp/>reveal<sp/>actual<sp/>values<sp/>to<sp/>untrusted<sp/>parties</highlight></codeline>
